<item>
            <title>[LU-8031] node-provisioning-1: giving a partition size of -0.26 from lvm</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8031</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for parinay &amp;lt;parinay_kondekar@xyratex.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/8c2b9a72-0305-11e6-9e5d-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/8c2b9a72-0305-11e6-9e5d-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test node-provisioning_1 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Failed to provision nodes: trevis-10vm11 lvm_info returned &apos;&apos; from  giving a partition size of -0.26 from lvm size 0.0 node info #&amp;lt;NodeInfo:0x007fe59e0dca38 @name=trevis-10vm11, @devices=[vda], @nettypes=[tcp], @partition_size_gb=-0.26, @nettype=tcp, @ger
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please provide additional information about the failure here.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: node-provisioning-1 node-provisioning_1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
